<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for By Shakir Luxury Interiors. Learn how we handle your personal data."
>
  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    By Shakir Luxury Interiors respects the privacy of all visitors to our website and treats any
    personal information you provide with care and confidentiality.
  </p>

  <h2>2. What data do we collect?</h2>
  <p>We only collect the details you voluntarily submit through our contact form:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number (if provided)</li>
    <li>Project type</li>
    <li>Your message</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How do we use your data?</h2>
  <p>Your data is only used to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Answer your question or request</li>
    <li>Contact you about your interior project</li>
    <li>Schedule a meeting if desired</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-party services</h2>
  <p>We use the following services:</p>

  <h3>Web3Forms</h3>
  <p>
    Our contact form submissions are processed via Web3Forms. Your data is securely transmitted to
    our email address. Web3Forms does not store your data permanently. More information:
    <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">web3forms.com/privacy</a>.
  </p>

  <h3>Cloudflare Web Analytics</h3>
  <p>
    We use Cloudflare Web Analytics for anonymous site statistics. It is privacy-friendly and does
    not set cookies. No personal data is collected or stored, and visitors are not tracked across
    sites.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Retention</h2>
  <p>
    Emails received via the contact form are kept only as long as necessary to handle your request
    or project, and are then deleted.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
    <li>Have your data corrected or deleted</li>
    <li>Object to the processing of your data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Security</h2>
  <p>
    We take appropriate security measures to prevent misuse and unauthorized access to your personal
    data. Our website uses a secure connection (HTTPS).
  </p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@byshakir.nl">info@byshakir.nl</a></li>
    <li>Phone: +31 344 655 473</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    By Shakir Luxury Interiors<br />
